## Limitations

This report is based on available literature and may not encompass all recent developments in climate science. The reliance on secondary sources means that some nuances of the primary research may not be fully captured. Additionally, the complexity of climate systems means that while human activities are a significant driver, natural factors also play a role, albeit to a lesser extent in recent decades.

